Package: csam
Type: Package
Title: Correlated Species Archetype Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Elliot", "Dovers", email = "elliot.dovers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Fits correlated species archetype models (CSAMs) via an ECM algorithm.
    The model is a finite mixture of generalized linear models with shared
    archetype-specific regression coefficients and a common factor-analytic
    term capturing residual species correlation via site scores and species
    loadings. Penalized likelihood estimation is used with ridge penalties on
    the factor scores and loadings.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
